*.jpeg

# Env
.env
.env.local

# Machine-specific MCP registration written by `careermate init` (absolute paths).
# Each user regenerates this with `npm run init`; never commit it.
.mcp.json

# Career-OS 교차검증은 R6/R7로 종료된 내부 R&D 로그다. 결론은 서술형 md로 증류해 git에 남기고,
# 기계 생성 원증거(JSON 영수증)와 재생성 가능한 하네스 입출력은 추적하지 않는다.
# git에 남기는 것(증류된 결정 기록): validation/{MANDATE,PROTOCOL,STATUS,README,APPLIED}.md,
#   validation/research/**, validation/runs/r7/{FIXES,ROUND7}.md.
# 추적 안 함(원증거·스크래치):
docs/career-os/validation/runs/consensus/
docs/career-os/validation/runs/ledger.jsonl
docs/career-os/validation/runs/r7/research-raw*.json
docs/career-os/validation/runs/out/
docs/career-os/validation/runs/calib/
docs/career-os/validation/runs/calib2/
docs/career-os/validation/runs/fixtures/
docs/career-os/validation/runs/negatives/
docs/career-os/validation/runs/bin/
docs/career-os/validation/runs/prompts/
docs/career-os/validation/runs/schema/
docs/career-os/validation/runs/_probe/
